{"tid":1327350,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"山本彩與IZ*ONE相見歡 為久違再見咲良感慨","createTime":"2019-07-17T14:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:15:17.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6c9772edeb9dea1735e7df02ce01ecd537b8d6","tid":1327350,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/07/190628060004100707-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F190628060004100707-600x400.jpg&h=efc09c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE第二張日文單曲《布宜諾斯艾利斯 (Buenos Aires)》形象照。<br />\n（c OFF THE RECORD／環球音樂提供）<br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣女團IZ*ONE成員宮脇咲良、金采源、金玟周（或譯珉周）及曹柔理，昨天（16日）晚間參與NHK的知名直播節目《うたコン》。成員們除了帶來KARA的《GO GO Summer!》等演出，同樣出身AKB48集團的宮脇咲良與山本彩的再會也受到關注。<br />\n<br />\n曾經擔任NMB48總隊長並曾兼任AKB48團員的山本彩，2018年11月自NMB48畢業並展開個人活動。在昨日的《うたコン》中，山本彩演唱了吉田拓郎的《暑假（夏休み）》，在節目中間的訪問及等待時間，她與目前因專注於IZ*ONE而暫停HKT48活動的宮脇咲良並肩而坐。<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE的四位成員，在13日的香港演唱會後並未隨其他成員回到韓國。她們在16日的節目中演唱了KARA的《GO GO Summer!》，采源及柔理還與日本知名歌手丘綠（丘みどり）共同帶來ZONE的《secret base～你給我的東西～（secret base～君がくれたもの～）》，有別於以往的特別演出也令粉絲感到驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n▼ 相關影片（來源：YouTube，如遭移除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hS9G-DQ3RN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhS9G-DQ3RN0&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQslznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=a5f23b74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hS9G-DQ3RN0</a><br />\n<br />\n而在節目結束後，山本彩於推特上傳了與IZ*ONE成員們的合照，並寫道：「播出結束後和IZ*ONE一起合照，也久違的能夠和咲良說說話，感慨萬千&hellip;&hellip;」該貼文也在一天內獲得超過3.6萬人按讚（愛心）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D_mXvh3UIAAcHWl.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD_mXvh3UIAAcHWl.jpg%3Alarge&h=1038e267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，昨日韓媒「Newsen」報導，選秀節目《PRODUCE 48》出身的IZ*ONE有望出席《PRODUCE X 101》於19日直播播出的最後一集總決賽。而宮脇咲良與矢吹奈子也將在24日參與日本富士電視台的「FNS夏日歌謠祭（FNSうたの夏まつり）」。IZ*ONE還將於27日參與「TGC TOYAMA 2019 by TOKYO GIRLS COLLECTION」演出。"},{"pid":"351a6c8f829aa1f054f8c127670975fc6115994a","tid":1327350,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"=&lt;=&lt;"},{"pid":"bc71856b9e62807e9040b39d67268c23a14e33c1","tid":1327350,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"( ‧ ) ( ‧ )"},{"pid":"5620b02fc79e48c1d2b23f90f1eccc46be47d1f6","tid":1327350,"uid":221236,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"每次見面猶如初見<br />\n感慨萬千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ca626312e2d39be2a9ca772dec41eb8d46bd3f","tid":1327350,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e686f54e27f949d6963d1655b105fb1daa5180f1","tid":1327350,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"5個入面牙周最靚"},{"pid":"647d49ef83e6f386366b0d74d488883011c0a8a1","tid":1327350,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e686f54e27f949d6963d1655b105fb1daa5180f1","tid":1327350,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"5個入面牙周最靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"非"},{"pid":"33757933617b1850cc70cdad994901f4ea08c965","tid":1327350,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647d49ef83e6f386366b0d74d488883011c0a8a1","tid":1327350,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e686f54e27f949d6963d1655b105fb1daa5180f1","tid":1327350,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"5個入面牙周最靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"非"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"